data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 2012-built house located in the highly desirable Harrison Ranch community! This gorgeous 3 bed 2 bath home with solar energy is truly move-in ready and has been recently painted inside! New Kitchen counter tops, bathroom vanities and carpet just added to entire house! As you enter the home, you are welcomed by an open-concept living room and plenty of natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen has wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, New Granite countertops updated in the kitchen and baths, and an ample closet pantry. The master bedroom is spacious and features an en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet with custom shelving. This home has a separate laundry room for your convenience and a great size backyard. With stunning curb appeal and a spacious layout, this home is perfect for families who enjoy both indoor and outdoor living. The amenities in this community are simply incredible, offering everything you need to stay active and entertained, like a gorgeous clubhouse with a fitness center, tennis courts, soccer fields, pickleball courts, and an Olympic-sized pool área! Located minutes from grocery stores, restaurants, and the Creekside Commons shopping plaza. Quick commute to Tampa, St. Pete, Bradenton, and Sarasota. Come see for yourself all that this property has to offer. Make an appointment today!
